API documentation - https://developer.riotgames.com/apis

What can be retrieved ? 
  - Game Status
  - Champions Rotations (both old and new players)
  - Active or Upcoming Tournaments
  - High Tier classament 
  - Champions Mastery (based on player ID)
  - Master Players
  - Games / Tournaments history
  - Active Game of a Summoner
  - Account Details (based on encrypted keys received upon search by Summoner Name / Region)
  - TFT High Tiers (Master / Grandmaster / Challenger)

Future: 
  - Valorant
